Next, I'll dive into the resolutions, focusing on "Sắp xếp các đơn vị hành chính cấp xã của tỉnh Đồng Tháp" (1663/NQ-UBTVQH15). This is where the real work begins. The issue is that the resolutions I have examined only contain mentions of Tân Thạnh in the context of huyện Thanh Bình, which is not what I'm looking for.

I'm starting to think this is a tricky one. The absence of a clear direct match in the resolutions has me concerned. I need to re-examine my approach and the data. It's time to refine my search strategy.
